src/blog/2023/view-transitions-first-experiments-mpa.md:68:This is a toy example, but it shows how powerful scoping transitions can be. Let's look at the HTML and CSS to make this happen. The [full code](https://github.com/tylergaw/mpa-view-transitions-sandbox/tree/main/unique-page-slide) is on Github.
